      "para_id": "Q001517.2",
      "line_range": "2",
      "translation": "(1') He mixed the clay in a pure place , and made the ( first ) brick in an undefiled place . He purified the foundation by carrying around fire , and anointed the foundation pegs with oil of princely fragrance ."
    }
  ],
